{"tid":1561482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［兄弟爬山］左膠撚表示9月區選提名期已到","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T09:51:13.000Z","uid":282058,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"e315fbe8dc53d517a166a09436cdaf447bcfeb99","tid":1561482,"uid":282058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"九月提名期已到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解無乜人開post講區選？<br />\n都已經九月中喇，啲文宣呢？<br />\n淨係識屌又唔諗下實質方法，<br />\n是咪又想俾禮義廉拎撚晒啲票啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.一定要打老人家戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民賤聯次次利用班老人家，掌心雷，蛇齋餅糭吸引佢地，你地班後生仔又唔同啲老人家解釋下社會狀況，又唔關心下屋企啲老友記，咁突然間有人向佢哋獻殷勤，佢哋梗係覺得有人關心佢哋，點都幫人哋啦，所以話其實老人家嘅票係好易拎返返嚟，正所謂票投民建聯香港玩撚完，今次我地係時候要搶返哂老人家既票數返嚟呀！！<br />\n<br />\n2. 老人家接觸既資訊太寡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日用埋晒we7，啲廢老群組成日send啲戇鳩文宣，又睇撚埋晒d深藍page乜鳩HKG報又乜柒港人講地，屌你老母洗撚晒啲呀伯呀婆腦。如果班老友記識睇下連登成件事會好唔同，至少唔會淨係單方面接受深藍資訊囉。<br />\n<br />\n3.有咩方法去對抗建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多啲關心老人家，噓寒問暖，多啲同老人家圍爐。我見Kickstarter 有得買本連登指南係專比老人家，啲吖公吖婆其實間唔中睇下連登好過比垃圾藍絲page洗鳩佢地個腦。古語有云：人一藍腦便殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以再比佢地繼續藍落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次一定唔可以再比民賤聯班撚樣贏，我地要搶返本來屬於我地既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ptgwaisuen/1265390473/description?fbclid=IwAR0Z7NKBYcFTQFM8WISK3bmjEHao9qKFT7eH-WqmJKQqmUgd1iiCTUnkGKU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fptgwaisuen%2F1265390473%2Fdescription%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Z7NKBYcFTQFM8WISK3bmjEHao9qKFT7eH-WqmJKQqmUgd1iiCTUnkGKU&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=fd2f4dd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ptgwaisuen/1265390473/description?fbclid=IwAR0Z7NKBYcFTQFM8WISK3bmjEHao9qKFT7eH-WqmJKQqmUgd1iiCTUnkGKU</a>"},{"pid":"c520c0ebb0ac73b7b094aca589c86b5e4baf3301","tid":1561482,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOSjYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOSjYn.jpg&h=c1edffca&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeMP6D2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai