佢貼地d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申買本被老母 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805521fafee59a2b95c67eedb3635a6d428ad490","tid":1561482,"uid":146909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe61c07c14f005732c19dd0d42e1db03ff8b842d","tid":1561482,"uid":82993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"買本被林奠，學下野，等佢貼地d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申買本被老母 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"真心成事之後送本比林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9629286a3ebbddc5bee560ab85a8a2aa36a66b44","tid":1561482,"uid":146909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一本送比林鄭</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4afc123eee3f06fde1b94c4a50f5f11182df2550","tid":1561482,"uid":154433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51df680b3019eda84da669fa0a45877d29fb4b97","tid":1561482,"uid":264626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"大家唔好放棄藍屍，有D唔係咁硬個D仲有得救。<br />\n<br />\n話說今日我亞媽 send 左呢條片比我，話覺得個大媽講得好啱，仲話以後唔會投民建聯（佢係民建聯區議員D義工）。我問佢邊個 send 比佢，佢話群組(民建聯義工群組）。我講笑話反了，反了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DPdqMbm7Ghw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDPdqMbm7Ghw&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=bc323152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DPdqMbm7Ghw</a><br />\n<br />\n講反D背景，我屋企兩老係大陸落左嚟幾十年，不過廣東話唔正，以前成日比人笑，可能因為咁掛，佢地D朋友，全部都係同鄕，做到朋友既同事都係大陸落嚟廣東話幾十年都講唔正個D，仲有熟既街坊亦多數係大陸落嚟個D（不過個區算係紅區）。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢地雖然落左嚟幾十年，生活已經完全融入香港，亦睇好多大陸人D無禮同污槽行為唔過眼，但內心可能覺得自己從來無被香港人接受（因為廣東話唔正），所以不自覺地同真香港人對立。<br />\n<br />\n但佢地其實係講道理既，只係唔會接觸到我地D文宣或睇蘋果個D，只係不斷比 cctvb 洗腦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n所以，除左長輩圖，係咪可以做D普通話、福建話、潮州話短片，掀發保皇當佢地儍仔扼佢地既真相片？一開始聽到自己熟悉既語言，可以吸引佢地睇落去。好似今日新聞，民主派一早係上年五月提出引用「收回土地條例」的法例收返D私人地比政府，以增加土地供應，但林鄭唔肯，話會引發私地業主司法覆核。根本以前有案例，唔會覆核好耐，但無論如何林鄭就唔接受民主派建議。今日，民建聯好似如夢初醒，突然賣報紙話要求政府引用民主派早係2018年提出既法例收地！係咪當人儍？點解之前唔支持依家先支持？到時林鄭答應，又變成民建聯的功勞，民建聯的「成功爭取」？真係好無恥。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7adc4658a4b9a6345b4bdbcbbe1b2b3fb60e6b65","tid":1561482,"uid":275093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd925bc556f2b9c514fbf2621df605e0eaca0159","tid":1561482,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"各區貼返自己文宣未"},{"pid":"3ddf250b1e25df012d244475f39b6bddc06d259c","tid":1561482,"uid":83989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得文宣要大力宣傳保皇黨班仆街點樣背叛投佢地票既選民  例如呢張圖 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go5M9uN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo5M9uN.jpg&h=dbda0cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋大家應該多啲同老人家傾下計<br />\n其實啲廢老都係因為得保皇啲垃圾關心，所以先會投比認識既人。<br />\n其實我地應該集中拉中間派票源"},{"pid":"4dcf7ee105f6c02d3be0abc33670283ec2fa78c2","tid":1561482,"uid":307783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a7bc7d381f8a2e752c4d6f876ec1118a065f3a68","tid":1561482,"uid":307783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":